com.skratchdot.riff.wav

Interface ChunkInstrument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Chunk
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChunkInstrumentImpl

    public interface ChunkInstrument
extends Chunk
    A representation of the model object 'Chunk Instrument'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Unshifted Note
    • Fine Tune
    • Gain
    • Low Note
    • High Note
    • Low Velocity
    • High Velocity

    See Also:
    WavPackage.getChunkInstrument()
